snippet.title: NEW Prototype N Demo (2023) is now out!
snippet.description:
DEMO LINKS:

hedgehogtechnicalinstitute.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=70 - INDIE'D Booth

https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/prototype-n-csage-2023-demo.1895/ - Christmas SAGExpo Booth

https://arrietty.itch.io/prototype-n - Itch Page

An armor of robots are rampaging across the world! Nadine, a prototype android of unknown origins, is set out to stop them while finding out who is her creator.

Prototype N is a side scrolling shooting platformer. Nadine is armed with a powerful arm cannon with the ability to swap between several destructive weapons to take down her foes. Some weapons may even lead her to secret paths. On top of that, one of her defining features is her Slide Attack. She can reach through narrow passages, make speed boosted jumps and even destroy grounded enemies with it.

This demo features contains Mega Man-like gameplay with 7 action packed levels, an exciting boss fight and 8 powerful weapons. Help Nadine save the world!
